#### Model Solution for Part (b) — 7 Marks

**System Architecture (2 marks):**

```
   ┌─────────────────┐                    ┌─────────────────┐
   │  CLIENT         │   TCP Connection  │  SERVER         │
   │  (127.0.0.1)    │◄─────────────────►│  (0.0.0.0:8080) │
